---
// 6. Interlude — the breath. Editorial pause that hands off from "philosophy"
// to "what's actually here." Visually distinct (different background tint,
// own borders) so it reads as a scene break.
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden border-y border-bone-500/15 bg-ink-50">
  <div class="container-page py-28 md:py-40">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-12 md:grid-cols-[auto_1fr] md:gap-16">
      <!-- Abstract: a single point, an arrow, and a constellation of nodes —
           the move from "solving one problem" to "navigating a space." -->
      <svg
        viewBox="0 0 200 200"
        fill="none"
        class="h-32 w-32 shrink-0 text-bone-200 md:h-44 md:w-44"
        aria-hidden="true"
        stroke="currentColor"
      >
        <circle cx="40" cy="100" r="6" fill="currentColor" />
        <line x1="50" y1="100" x2="120" y2="100" stroke-width="0.8" />
        <path
          d="M 110 92 L 122 100 L 110 108"
          stroke-width="0.8"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
        />
        <line x1="135" y1="100" x2="160" y2="60" stroke-width="0.6" />
        <line x1="135" y1="100" x2="170" y2="115" stroke-width="0.6" />
        <line x1="135" y1="100" x2="155" y2="155" stroke-width="0.6" />
        <line x1="160" y1="60" x2="170" y2="115" stroke-width="0.5" />
        <line x1="170" y1="115" x2="155" y2="155" stroke-width="0.5" />
        <circle cx="135" cy="100" r="3" fill="currentColor" />
        <circle cx="160" cy="60" r="4" fill="currentColor" />
        <circle cx="170" cy="115" r="5" fill="currentColor" />
        <circle cx="155" cy="155" r="3" fill="currentColor" />
      </svg>

      <div>
        <p class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-bone-300">
          Interlude
        </p>
        <p
          class="mt-6 max-w-[26ch] text-[36px] font-semibold leading-[1.05] tracking-tightest text-bone-0 md:text-[64px] md:leading-[1.02]"
          style="text-wrap: balance;"
        >
          Solving was the question. Choosing is the new one.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
